question: Dame un ranking detallado con percentiles de proveedores que hayan contratado con la municipalidad distrital de los olivos en los años 2021, 2022 y 2023. Quiero las columnas de tipo de contrato, la cantidad, el monto promedio, la desviacion estandar, el monto minimo, el monto maximo, el percentil 25, la mediana, el percentil 75 y el percentil 95. Considera usar un IN para los años.
query: SELECT tipo_contrato, COUNT(*) as cantidad, AVG(monto) as monto_promedio, STDDEV(monto) as desviacion_estandar, MIN(monto) as monto_minimo, MAX(monto) as monto_maximo, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.25) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as percentil_25, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.50) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as mediana, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.75) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as percentil_75, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as percentil_95 FROM contratos_orden_servicio WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fecha_inicio) IN (2021,2022,2023) AND entidad_contratante ILIKE '%MUNICIPALIDAD DISTRITAL DE LOS OLIVOS%' GROUP BY tipo_contrato;

baseline_template.sql_query: SELECT nombre_proveedor, COUNT(*) as num_contratos, SUM(monto) as monto_total FROM contratos_orden_servicio WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fecha_inicio) = CAST('2021' AS INTEGER) GROUP BY nombre_proveedor ORDER BY monto_total DESC LIMIT 10;

baseline_agent_simple.sql_query: SELECT co.tipo_contrato, COUNT(*) AS cantidad, AVG(co.monto) AS monto_promedio, STDDEV(co.monto) AS desviacion_estandar, MIN(co.monto) AS monto_minimo, MAX(co.monto) AS monto_maximo, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.25) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY co.monto) AS percentil_25, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY co.monto) AS mediana, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.75) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY co.monto) AS percentil_75, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY co.monto) AS percentil_95 FROM contratos_orden_servicio co WHERE co.entidad_contratante ILIKE '%municipalidad distrital de los olivos%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM co.fecha_inicio) IN (2021, 2022, 2023) GROUP BY co.tipo_contrato ORDER BY co.tipo_contrato;

our_agent.sql_query: WITH contratos_los_olivos AS ( SELECT c.ruc_proveedor, c.nombre_proveedor, c.tipo_contrato, c.monto, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM c.fecha_inicio) as año FROM contratos_orden_servicio c WHERE UPPER(c.entidad_contratante) LIKE '%MUNICIPALIDAD DISTRITAL DE LOS OLIVOS%' AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM c.fecha_inicio) IN (2021, 2022, 2023) AND c.monto IS NOT NULL ), estadisticas_por_proveedor AS ( SELECT ruc_proveedor, nombre_proveedor, tipo_contrato, COUNT(*) as cantidad_contratos, AVG(monto) as monto_promedio, STDDEV(monto) as desviacion_estandar, MIN(monto) as monto_minimo, MAX(monto) as monto_maximo, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.25) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as percentil_25, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.50) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as mediana, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.75) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as percentil_75, PERCENTILE_CONT(0.95) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY monto) as percentil_95, SUM(monto) as monto_total FROM contratos_los_olivos GROUP BY ruc_proveedor, nombre_proveedor, tipo_contrato ) SELECT ruc_proveedor, nombre_proveedor, tipo_contrato, cantidad_contratos, ROUND(monto_promedio::numeric, 2) as monto_promedio, ROUND(COALESCE(desviacion_estandar, 0)::numeric, 2) as desviacion_estandar, ROUND(monto_minimo::numeric, 2) as monto_minimo, ROUND(monto_maximo::numeric, 2) as monto_maximo, ROUND(percentil_25::numeric, 2) as percentil_25, ROUND(mediana::numeric, 2) as mediana, ROUND(percentil_75::numeric, 2) as percentil_75, ROUND(percentil_95::numeric, 2) as percentil_95, ROUND(monto_total::numeric, 2) as monto_total FROM estadisticas_por_proveedor ORDER BY monto_total DESC, cantidad_contratos DESC;
